<Base title="Privacy Policy | Bliss Coach" description="How Bliss Coach apps (Sofia, Amélie, Charm, Alex, Mila, Astra) collect, use, and protect your data." bodyClass="article-page">
  <article>
    <header class="article-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated July 2, 2026</p>
    </header>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>This policy describes how Bliss Coach ("we") handles your information across our iOS applications — Sofia, Amélie, Charm, Alex, Mila and Astra — and this website.</p>
      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account information</strong>: the display name and sign-in identifier (e.g. Apple ID relay email) you provide when creating an account.</li>
        <li><strong>Content you share in the app</strong>: messages, voice audio processed for transcription, and — where the feature exists — images you choose to upload. This content is used to generate the coaching responses you ask for.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage and diagnostics</strong>: feature usage events, crash reports, and device information, used to fix bugs and improve the product.</li>
        <li><strong>Subscription status</strong>: managed by Apple and our subscription infrastructure (RevenueCat). We never see or store your payment card details.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>To provide and improve the coaching experience, personalize sessions, maintain your progress (streaks, history), provide support, and measure aggregate product performance. AI responses are generated by third-party AI providers acting as processors; your conversations are not used by us to train foundation models.</p>
      <h2>Sharing</h2>
      <p>We share data only with service providers needed to run the apps (cloud hosting, AI inference, speech synthesis, analytics, subscription management) under their respective data-processing terms. We do not sell your personal data.</p>
      <h2>Retention &amp; deletion</h2>
      <p>You can delete your account at any time from Settings inside each app, which removes your personal data from our systems. You can also contact us for deletion requests.</p>
      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on where you live (including under GDPR), you may have rights to access, correct, export, or erase your data. Contact us to exercise them.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Bliss Coach — <a href="mailto:anthony@blisscoach.app">anthony@blisscoach.app</a></p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
